      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with its signature individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is mechanically sound, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a recently refreshed suspension with polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a precision valve clearance adjustment. While the exterior and interior show the honest patina of an enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust, offering the visceral, analog feedback this chassis is legendary for.",
